## **Adept**
**_Prerequisite: 5th level_**

_Each ability costs 2 talent points_

**Abilities:**
- **Earthen Resilience:** Gain proficiency in Constitution saving throws.
- **Terramancer:** Gain expertise (double proficiency bonus) in Athletics when performing tasks involving lifting, pushing, or pulling heavy objects made of stone or earth.
- **Stone Camouflage:** You have advantage on Stealth checks to hide in rocky terrain or against stone surfaces.
- **Earthen Grasp:** You can use an action to cause the ground to grasp a creature within 30 feet, restraining it for 1 minute. The target can make a Strength saving throw at the end of each of its turns to break free. You can use this feature after a long res
- **Stone Armor:** As a bonus action, you can encase yourself in a layer of stone, granting you resistance to bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing damage for 1 minute. You can use this feature after a short or long rest.
- **Sandstorm:** You can use an action to create a swirling storm of sand in a 20-foot radius centered on you. Creatures in the area must make a Constitution saving throw or be blinded until the end of their next turn. You can use this feature after a long rest.

**3rd Level Spells:**
- [Erupting Earth](https://5e.tools/spells.html#erupting%20earth_xge)
- [Wall of Sand](https://5e.tools/spells.html#wall%20of%20sand_xge)
- [Meld into Stone](https://5e.tools/spells.html#meld%20into%20stone_phb)

**4th Level Spells:**
- [Stone Shape](https://5e.tools/spells.html#stone%20shape_phb)
- [Stoneskin](https://5e.tools/spells.html#stoneskin_phb)
